{"tid":2422157,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安心出行 會自動核實QR code是否經由政府發出 其他來源的 QR code無效","createTime":"2021-02-25T04:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:18:43.000Z","uid":178875,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c46ede2bc524a17c0c493f640a5ec037de116c5","tid":2422157,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"日常生活中，大家經常都需要用手機掃描QR code，例如購物消費、搭車付款、用「安心出行」記錄行程等等，不過掃Code之前，有否想過有寫QR code可能是假冒？政府資訊科技總監辦公室提醒大家，<span class=\"red\">不用擔心「安心出行」掃到假QR code，因為程式會自動核實QR code是否「真貨」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資科辦在Facebook專頁表示，大家進入食肆或處所時用「安心出行」掃場所的QR code，大可放心，因為「安心出行」會自動核實QR code是否經由政府發出，然後才幫市民記下出行紀錄。如果發覺是其他來源的 QR code，就會顯示QR code無效。資科辦提醒大家提高警覺，只掃描來源可靠的QR code，以及用相關的應用程式來掃碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/hd/7e13a081dbda78bcb21523e1b6b51e7f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210224/_2021022418015734631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F7e13a081dbda78bcb21523e1b6b51e7f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210224%2F_2021022418015734631.jpg&h=2861cfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班港獨份子唔會阻止到我用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc95a8ccbe35ec3b096e215208af9613d0678e19","tid":2422157,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"好驚好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9509cc7f8823a11504b0ed35be099dd62114e6","tid":2422157,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:18:41.000Z","ms